title: American Horror Story Weekly Wednesday Live Stream
author: MaryGirl Moody
comment: I keep thinking of Dune, when pregnant Lady Jessica undergoes the Spice agony ritual she drinks water and her unborn baby gains all the knowledge of the universe and is immediately born with ALL THE TALENT. I think Doris will take a pill after Denis O’Hare’s fabulous character critiques her boring design work and the talented baby will want out!
Thank you. So glad to place a face to all these amazing reviews. Thanks for the insightful, intelligent reviews.
Eisenhower will be the president in the Death Valley story. According to what has been released officially that story will be a completely separate story from Red Tide but I guess we'll see.
I don’t think this will happen but honestly I would be thrilled if Doris took a pill and the baby WASN’T talented so it instantly turned into a pale person and clawed it’s way out!
Mary! I finally got power and internet back after hurricane Ida.
